snippet.title: Orisinal: Winterbells - Trying to beat my old high score
snippet.description:
I've definitely had higher scores on older computers, but it's just kind of fun to play. I just love the song and the cute bunny and it's my favorite of all the games on the site.

You can play it here: http://www.ferryhalim.com/orisinal/g3/bells.htm

Youtube Membership: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCr_vdRz1iA9St9wyNhlvm_A/join

♥ My website (for reviews, game blogs, and various other articles): http://www.crystal-dreams.us
